1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
=Legend of Fei=

16
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 33=

17
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,680
Precisely!

18
00:01:34,830 --> 00:01:36,120
We’re shameless.

19
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,760
But being defeated will
bring more disgrace to him.

20
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:40,510
Being shameless would be better!

21
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:42,910
Sir.

22
00:01:42,910 --> 00:01:44,190
We’re really confronting
some shameless men.

23
00:01:44,190 --> 00:01:45,270
What do we do?

24
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:47,540
(Animal characters made by CG)

25
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:51,950
(Animal characters made by CG)

26
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:53,360
Hongyu is warning us.

27
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,830
Li Yan is in danger.

28
00:01:54,860 --> 00:01:56,100
(Animal characters made by CG)

29
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,480
Old man.

30
00:02:03,630 --> 00:02:04,480
Don’t you think so?

31
00:02:12,190 --> 00:02:12,880
Come on.

32
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:16,320
Why do you all want to butt in?

33
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:18,630
(Animal characters made by CG)
Lord, snakes on the ground!

34
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:22,440
Snakes! Run!

35
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:28,540
(Animal characters made by CG)

36
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:30,520
Wait. Wait and see!

37
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:37,080
(Animal characters made by CG)
Go. Go!

38
00:02:38,670 --> 00:02:40,270
You, Poisoner Ying Hecong.

39
00:02:40,270 --> 00:02:41,800
Wait and see!

40
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:46,190
(Animal characters made by CG)
Go, hurry. Go!

41
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,600
Hyah.

42
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,160
Miss.

43
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:01,030
This is the best horse I sell.

44
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,160
Can it go up to the snow mountain?

45
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,470
Yes, it can.

46
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:09,320
Look what a strong horse it is!

47
00:03:09,670 --> 00:03:10,670
Throughout the town,

48
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:13,240
you can’t find a better one.

49
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,190
You don’t believe me?

50
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:15,670
Go check other horses, then.

51
00:03:16,470 --> 00:03:18,440
Forget it. I don’t have time.
I’ll take this one.

52
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,910
Hyah. Go.

53
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:25,910
Miss, wish you a nice trip.

54
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,750
I’ve done

55
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:39,720
what you asked me to do.

56
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,390
The horse I sold to that girl

57
00:03:41,390 --> 00:03:42,910
looks good,

58
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:45,160
but it isn’t cold-resistant at all.

59
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,030
It won’t make it to the snow mountain.

60
00:03:55,580 --> 00:04:00,860
(Hearing Ox, Lu Tiankuang
of Demons Manor)

61
00:04:17,580 --> 00:04:20,900
(Lanruo Temple)

62
00:04:28,660 --> 00:04:31,260
(Lanruo Temple)

63
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,270
(Lanruo Temple)
Don’t bother about me.

64
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:42,040
Go your own way.

65
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,160
Leave me alone. Go away!

66
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,880
We risked our lives to save you!

67
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:46,950
Why are you so ungrateful?

68
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:48,720
Go knock on the door.

69
00:04:51,550 --> 00:04:52,550
Go.

70
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,000
Sir.

71
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,510
I know you don’t want to be our burden.

72
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:08,600
But it’s too late

73
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,950
to go separate ways.

74
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:10,880
The Demons have already

75
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,920
pin it on us.

76
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:15,040
So, you’d better take a rest first.

77
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,720
I don’t care where you’re going.

78
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,160
But if you still want to live,

79
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,480
you must get healed immediately.

80
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,110
Otherwise,

81
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:37,480
we could just find a place

82
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,670
and bury you.

83
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,110
Ying Hecong.

84
00:05:40,110 --> 00:05:41,880
Have you ever annoyed a patient
to death?

85
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,510
Don’t worry.

86
00:05:44,070 --> 00:05:46,350
(Lanruo Temple)
I’ve got something to do.

87
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:47,880
I won’t die for the moment.

88
00:05:48,160 --> 00:05:49,040
But if

89
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:52,230
you’re also after the secret,

90
00:05:53,670 --> 00:05:54,720
you’d better not

91
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:57,920
make futile efforts.

92
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,760
Forget it.

93
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:01,350
A secret made so many people
hunt you down.

94
00:06:01,350 --> 00:06:02,880
We’d better not know it.

95
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:05,110
Sir, trust us.

96
00:06:05,110 --> 00:06:06,200
If the Demons want to kill someone,

97
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,510
we save him!

98
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:10,440
Ask him, if you don’t believe me.

99
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,550
Ying Hecong.

100
00:06:11,550 --> 00:06:13,510
The Demons are your enemies, right?

101
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,320
Their enemy

102
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:15,830
must be our friend, right?

103
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:18,640
I’ll at least be alive to take revenge.

104
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,670
You’re so good at making trouble.

105
00:06:20,670 --> 00:06:22,200
I’m afraid I can’t live so long.

106
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,270
I think no one is in.

107
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:29,440
No one?

108
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:38,230
Then who closed the door?

109
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:39,790
Get out of the way.
I’ll split open the door.

110
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:41,640
Yeah, Bonehead.

111
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,390
You can just use your firewood chopper.

112
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:43,920
Go.

113
00:06:44,550 --> 00:06:46,550
I’ll split you, don’t you believe?

114
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:50,950
Who...?

115
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:52,920
Who are you?

116
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:01,350
Come out. They’re not bad men.

117
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,950
Don’t be scared. Come out.

118
00:07:24,670 --> 00:07:30,350
Hyah! Hyah!

119
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:32,790
Lord.

120
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:34,640
According to the horseshoe marks,

121
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,440
they went this way.

122
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,160
After them!

123
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:37,920
Hyah!

124
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,830
The wound has been dressed.

125
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:42,230
You’re no longer bleeding, too.

126
00:07:42,230 --> 00:07:44,270
You’re just children.

127
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:46,440
Why are you all hiding
in such a shabby temple?

128
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,270
We’re schoolmates.

129
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:52,000
We went to the same school
in our hometown.

130
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,720
War broke out there.

131
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,230
Our villagers ran away.

132
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:59,110
Our parents and we lost each other.

133
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:02,760
Luckily, we met a kind teacher

134
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,440
who led us forward.

135
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,880
He said there was no war in the south.

136
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:09,000
He had planned to take us to the south.

137
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,950
We found this shabby temple on our way

138
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:12,950
as a temporary shelter.

139
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:14,950
Where is the teacher, then?

140
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:17,230
Hearing that the Demons came around,

141
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:18,830
he’s gone out to see what’s happening.

142
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,670
He’ll be back soon, I guess.

143
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:24,880
Wait.

144
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:28,390
You just said there was no war
in the south?

145
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:30,480
Hou Jian is dead?

146
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,640
What about His Majesty?

147
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,150
What about Governor Huang?

148
00:08:33,930 --> 00:08:35,440
Who is Hou Jian?

149
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,390
Who is Governor Huang?

150
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:40,470
I heard of him from the teacher.

151
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:43,320
Hou Jian was a rebel
against the former dynasty.

152
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:46,240
But he’s been dead
for over twenty years.

153
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,440
Sir, is this the man you asked about?

154
00:08:49,450 --> 00:08:50,300
You’re dying.

155
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:51,050
What the hell are you doing?

156
00:08:53,010 --> 00:08:54,100
You just said the former dynasty?

157
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:58,370
Hou Jian has been dead?

158
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:02,690
Who is the emperor in the south now?

159
00:09:02,690 --> 00:09:05,450
Sir, what’s wrong with you?

160
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:08,570
Emperor Xuan, of course.

161
00:09:08,570 --> 00:09:11,370
Who is that? What about His Majesty?

162
00:09:13,450 --> 00:09:15,690
What about Governor Huang Shenbian?

163
00:09:15,690 --> 00:09:17,690
Huang Shenbian?

164
00:09:18,370 --> 00:09:20,980
I heard of him from my uncle.

165
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:23,930
But he’s also been dead
for over twenty years.

166
00:09:28,930 --> 00:09:31,660
Governor Huang fought hard

167
00:09:32,130 --> 00:09:33,930
and pledged to defend His Majesty.

168
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:36,610
But they’re all dead?

169
00:09:39,130 --> 00:09:40,780
The Xiao family is gone.

170
00:09:41,570 --> 00:09:43,050
His Majesty is gone.

171
00:09:46,540 --> 00:09:49,780
That explains. That explains.

172
00:09:49,780 --> 00:09:52,930
Sir, did you break your head

173
00:09:52,930 --> 00:09:54,780
when you fell?

174
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:57,050
Let’s go.

175
00:09:57,050 --> 00:09:59,370
The Demons will easily catch up
according to the horseshoe marks.

176
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:00,930
Go, or it’ll be too late.

177
00:10:02,130 --> 00:10:04,340
Sir, your wound has been dressed.

178
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,420
Let’s go.

179
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:07,610
No!

180
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:09,610
So many children in the temple.

181
00:10:09,610 --> 00:10:11,050
Can they leave?

182
00:10:11,050 --> 00:10:12,980
If the Demons track us down,

183
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:13,980
they must know

184
00:10:13,980 --> 00:10:15,610
we’ve come this way.

185
00:10:15,610 --> 00:10:17,050
If they fail to find us,

186
00:10:17,050 --> 00:10:18,420
they will hurt these children,

187
00:10:18,420 --> 00:10:20,740
considering how evil they are.

188
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:22,370
They’re after us!

189
00:10:22,370 --> 00:10:23,810
Why will they hurt these children?

190
00:10:23,810 --> 00:10:25,930
If the Demons were
as simple-minded as you,

191
00:10:25,930 --> 00:10:27,300
the world would have been in peace.

192
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:31,010
Sir.

193
00:10:31,010 --> 00:10:32,930
If the Demons break in,

194
00:10:32,930 --> 00:10:34,610
we’ll try to hold them back.

195
00:10:34,660 --> 00:10:35,690
You can run away

196
00:10:35,690 --> 00:10:36,740
with these children.

197
00:10:36,810 --> 00:10:37,900
Girl.

198
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:40,570
You don’t even know who I am.

199
00:10:41,130 --> 00:10:43,220
Why do you help me?

200
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:46,900
You don’t need to fight the Demons

201
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:49,420
for a mere stranger.

202
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:52,900
We, the Fortress of the Forty-Eight,

203
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:54,420
have fought the Demons many times.

204
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:56,180
Fortress of the Forty-Eight?

205
00:10:56,570 --> 00:10:57,370
Who...?

206
00:11:00,130 --> 00:11:03,100
Who is Li Zheng to you?

207
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,610
You know my grandfather?

208
00:11:06,370 --> 00:11:07,010
Sir.

209
00:11:09,810 --> 00:11:11,860
We risked our lives
to keep you safe all the way.

210
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:13,810
Now you know who we are.

211
00:11:13,810 --> 00:11:15,740
Shouldn’t you tell us who you are?

212
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:18,100
I’m Liu Youliang.

213
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:20,180
I’m just an old grave keeper,

214
00:11:20,860 --> 00:11:23,860
unknown to the public.

215
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:26,010
The Demons sent Tong Tianyang

216
00:11:26,010 --> 00:11:27,900
for a mere grave keeper?

217
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:30,300
What if there’s treasure in the grave

218
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:33,900
that can conquer the whole world?

219
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:34,900
Treasure.

220
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:38,250
Treasure?

221
00:11:39,130 --> 00:11:41,220
Girl, come over.

222
00:11:41,780 --> 00:11:42,300
Don’t go.

223
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:46,570
Sir, you haven’t answered

224
00:11:46,570 --> 00:11:48,010
our question yet.

225
00:11:48,010 --> 00:11:49,300
Who exactly are you?

226
00:11:49,930 --> 00:11:52,540
You’re so anxious about my identity?

227
00:11:52,570 --> 00:11:54,450
My identity doesn’t matter.

228
00:11:54,450 --> 00:11:56,900
What I’ve been guarding matters most!

229
00:11:57,570 --> 00:12:00,690
I’m a bodyguard
of Governor Huang Shenbian.

230
00:12:00,690 --> 00:12:02,980
When putting down the rebellion,

231
00:12:02,980 --> 00:12:04,900
Governor Huang transferred me
out of the army,

232
00:12:04,900 --> 00:12:06,690
to guard something,

233
00:12:06,690 --> 00:12:09,370
named the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

234
00:12:11,300 --> 00:12:13,050
-The Color of Ocean and Heaven again?
-The Color of Ocean and Heaven again?

235
00:12:13,980 --> 00:12:15,180
Yeah.

236
00:12:15,180 --> 00:12:18,050
Your grandfather was
one of the guardians.

237
00:12:18,810 --> 00:12:22,010
You must have heard of it.

238
00:12:22,010 --> 00:12:23,660
Governor Huang said

239
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:26,300
he would send someone
with the ripple-shaped object

240
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:28,690
after putting down the rebellion.

241
00:12:28,930 --> 00:12:32,130
I would help to get out
the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

242
00:12:32,810 --> 00:12:33,930
Unexpectedly,

243
00:12:34,570 --> 00:12:37,570
I waited for over twenty years.

244
00:12:38,450 --> 00:12:40,300
Over twenty years?

245
00:12:40,300 --> 00:12:42,900
Sir, were you all alone

246
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:44,740
during these years?

247
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:47,340
Yeah, I was all alone.

248
00:12:47,860 --> 00:12:48,570
No.

249
00:12:50,570 --> 00:12:54,570
I don’t even know what I am now,

250
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:57,370
a lonely human or a ghost?

251
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:19,050
All right.

252
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:21,980
After giving him some energy

253
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:23,100
and feeding him the decoction,

254
00:13:24,010 --> 00:13:27,450
we can finally keep him alive
for the moment.

255
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:39,860
Tongming.

256
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:41,660
How long can the decoction effect last?

257
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:43,780
As far as I see,

258
00:13:44,810 --> 00:13:46,450
one month, at most.

259
00:13:46,450 --> 00:13:48,010
(Chen Junfu, Immortal of Penglai)
You must be kidding.

260
00:13:48,010 --> 00:13:49,980
Even if you go personally,

261
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:51,300
it’ll take more than one month
to get the Fire Lotus.

262
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:53,300
Not to mention that young girl.

263
00:13:54,050 --> 00:13:55,340
I trust her.

264
00:13:55,930 --> 00:13:58,130
If she can’t come back in one month,

265
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:59,130
how...

266
00:13:59,130 --> 00:14:00,250
how can we help Anzhi?

267
00:14:01,130 --> 00:14:02,860
It’s her predestined fate.

268
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:04,180
It’s also Anzhi’s.

269
00:14:15,610 --> 00:14:17,010
The Three-kind Decoction

270
00:14:17,570 --> 00:14:20,780
will force out his last vitality

271
00:14:20,780 --> 00:14:22,450
so that he won’t be a cold dead body

272
00:14:22,450 --> 00:14:24,860
without any movement.

273
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:27,300
But after taking one dose,

274
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:28,810
he’ll lose some vitality.

275
00:14:29,930 --> 00:14:31,180
After taking three doses,

276
00:14:31,930 --> 00:14:34,050
if we still can’t find the antidote...

277
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:37,980
Then why did you use
such a strong decoction?

