have travelled for years,

285
00:14:56,010 --> 00:14:57,780
but haven’t found any clue.

286
00:14:57,810 --> 00:15:00,130
Big Medicine Valley has been destroyed,

287
00:15:00,130 --> 00:15:02,050
even without a single heir.

288
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:07,780
Maybe the Book of Almighty Medicine

289
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:10,220
was burnt into ashes

290
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:11,740
in the fire of Big Medicine Valley.

291
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:46,690
Go!

292
00:15:53,540 --> 00:15:54,570
Go!

293
00:15:58,010 --> 00:15:59,010
Go!

294
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:08,420
Forget it.

295
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:10,050
Since you don’t want to go,

296
00:16:10,050 --> 00:16:11,570
wait here for me.

297
00:17:44,330 --> 00:17:45,180
Excuse me.

298
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:50,090
Did you see a girl
with a long blade on her back?

299
00:17:50,730 --> 00:17:51,490
Yes.

300
00:17:52,610 --> 00:17:54,060
Did she go that away?

301
00:17:54,580 --> 00:17:55,370
Yes.

302
00:17:55,610 --> 00:17:57,730
I’ve never seen
such a stubborn girl like her.

303
00:17:59,130 --> 00:18:00,610
Do you know her?

304
00:18:00,610 --> 00:18:02,730
It’s very dangerous over there.

305
00:18:03,370 --> 00:18:05,010
There was a snowstorm, wasn’t there?

306
00:18:05,820 --> 00:18:06,490
Yeah.

307
00:18:08,850 --> 00:18:10,090
How did you know?

308
00:18:10,090 --> 00:18:11,460
You’re native?

309
00:18:12,460 --> 00:18:13,970
After the snowstorm,

310
00:18:13,970 --> 00:18:15,490
there’s always an avalanche.

311
00:18:16,660 --> 00:18:18,490
She’s just in time.

312
00:18:21,420 --> 00:18:22,700
You know there was a snowstorm

313
00:18:22,700 --> 00:18:23,660
and you’re still going up the mountain?

314
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:24,850
Are you trying to kill yourself?

315
00:18:27,850 --> 00:18:29,330
Will a wolf of the snow mountain

316
00:18:29,370 --> 00:18:30,820
fear the snowstorm?

317
00:18:41,900 --> 00:18:45,780
Are...? Are you...?

318
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:47,540
Snow Wolf?

319
00:18:48,780 --> 00:18:49,780
It’s said

320
00:18:49,780 --> 00:18:51,420
that you grew up in a wolf’s den,

321
00:18:54,330 --> 00:18:56,940
Snow Wolf is back! Snow Wolf is back!

322
00:18:57,780 --> 00:19:01,970
Snow Wolf is back! Snow Wolf is back!

323
00:19:07,090 --> 00:19:08,370
At first,

324
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:10,580
Mr. Chongxiao and I

325
00:19:10,580 --> 00:19:13,010
often wrote letters to each other.

326
00:19:13,940 --> 00:19:14,900
But...

327
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:17,940
He never told me

328
00:19:18,850 --> 00:19:20,700
there was a new emperor.

329
00:19:21,490 --> 00:19:23,090
I think

330
00:19:23,090 --> 00:19:26,730
he doesn’t want me to leave
without permission.

331
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:29,250
What is

332
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:30,820
the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

333
00:19:30,820 --> 00:19:32,850
So many people died to guard it.

334
00:19:34,010 --> 00:19:35,900
The saddest part is

335
00:19:36,730 --> 00:19:38,900
after guarding it for over twenty years,

336
00:19:39,780 --> 00:19:41,850
I still don’t know what it is.

337
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:45,250
Nor do I know

338
00:19:46,580 --> 00:19:47,780
who I should give it to.

339
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:50,300
Well, this is life.

340
00:19:51,010 --> 00:19:52,540
Well, it’s not the worst.

341
00:19:53,130 --> 00:19:54,730
These days,

342
00:19:54,730 --> 00:19:57,090
Mr. Chongxiao hasn’t written to me.

343
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:02,180
You can’t imagine

344
00:20:02,180 --> 00:20:04,210
how I felt.

345
00:20:04,210 --> 00:20:05,420
It was so quiet.

346
00:20:07,780 --> 00:20:09,300
Around me,

347
00:20:09,300 --> 00:20:12,460
there were only ghosts and wind.

348
00:20:14,090 --> 00:20:17,180
I couldn’t help leaving that place,

349
00:20:17,180 --> 00:20:19,730
trying to find Mr. Chongxiao.

350
00:20:20,460 --> 00:20:22,180
Mr. Chongxiao?

351
