I heard of him from my brother.

352
00:20:25,250 --> 00:20:26,180
He knew Mr. Chongxiao.

353
00:20:27,250 --> 00:20:28,730
When we’re out of trouble,

354
00:20:28,730 --> 00:20:30,730
I’ll ask my brother to look for him.

355
00:20:32,490 --> 00:20:33,970
