appeared again.

358
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:40,780
It’s something

359
00:20:40,780 --> 00:20:43,540
Governor Huang tried hard to hide.

360
00:20:43,540 --> 00:20:44,900
But it was discussed in public

361
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:47,900
at the funny
Demon-Extermination Assembly.

362
00:20:48,420 --> 00:20:50,940
How ridiculous!

363
00:20:53,460 --> 00:20:55,820
I had planned to go to the Assembly

364
00:20:55,820 --> 00:20:58,370
and see what was happening.

365
00:20:58,900 --> 00:20:59,900
Unexpectedly,

366
00:21:00,850 --> 00:21:02,580
an old acquaintance from the palace

367
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:04,940
found me.

368
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:07,420
The Demons

369
00:21:07,850 --> 00:21:09,580
