370
00:21:10,940 --> 00:21:12,820
You mean Chu Tianyu?

371
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:16,780
Girl, you know a lot.

372
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:20,970
My cousin and Ying Hecong killed him.

373
00:21:20,970 --> 00:21:22,130
I certainly know him.

374
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:27,300
Something is wrong.

375
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:30,540
They’re catching up.

376
00:21:30,540 --> 00:21:32,370
Girl, take this.

377
00:21:32,370 --> 00:21:33,330
Sir.

378
00:21:33,330 --> 00:21:34,460
What’s this?

379
00:21:35,580 --> 00:21:36,660
Recite it.

380
00:21:37,370 --> 00:21:39,540
What’s the red part?

381
00:21:39,540 --> 00:21:41,060
Recite the poem at the back.

382
00:21:42,060 --> 00:21:42,970
Poem?

383
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:46,500
(Send stones to the north of the river
and climb the mountain for Ganoderma.)

384
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:49,730
I’m ordered
to guard the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

385
00:21:49,730 --> 00:21:51,090
Except me,

386
00:21:51,090 --> 00:21:51,900
no other living men

387
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:54,210
know its location.

388
00:21:56,180 --> 00:21:57,460
Now,

389
00:21:57,460 --> 00:22:00,130
I’m giving this secret to you.

390
00:22:00,130 --> 00:22:01,660
Recite the map,

391
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:05,820
so that the Color of Ocean and Heaven
won’t disappear.

392
00:22:06,330 --> 00:22:08,090
The hard work of a generation

393
00:22:08,540 --> 00:22:10,940
will not be wasted.

394
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:16,460
-Hyah.
-Hyah.

395
00:22:16,460 --> 00:22:17,920
(Music comes everywhere
when four songs are played.)

396
00:22:17,930 --> 00:22:19,380
(The valley is beautiful
where birds sing beautifully.)

397
00:22:19,380 --> 00:22:20,460
(Send stones to the north of the river
and climb the mountain for Ganoderma.)

398
00:22:20,470 --> 00:22:21,500
(I go to Wuzhou to see you
where mountains appear at dusk.)

399
00:22:21,580 --> 00:22:22,580
Kids.

400
00:22:22,940 --> 00:22:24,780
No matter what happens,

401
00:22:24,780 --> 00:22:26,660
