00:22:29,540 --> 00:22:30,460
(Lanruo Temple)

403
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:32,420
(Lanruo Temple)

404
00:22:41,210 --> 00:22:44,420
Get out of the way and let them leave.

405
00:22:44,420 --> 00:22:45,460
Otherwise,

406
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:48,010
I’ll tear the map!

407
00:22:48,580 --> 00:22:49,660
Fine. Fine.

408
00:22:49,660 --> 00:22:51,130
Don’t be nervous.

409
00:22:51,130 --> 00:22:52,300
Liu Youliang,

410
00:22:52,300 --> 00:22:54,660
give me the map,

411
00:22:54,660 --> 00:22:56,250
and I’ll let them go.

412
00:22:56,250 --> 00:22:58,460
Sir, don’t give it to them.

413
00:22:58,460 --> 00:22:59,820
If you do, we can’t leave!

414
00:22:59,820 --> 00:23:00,300
Shut up!

415
00:23:01,090 --> 00:23:02,490
Do...? Do you think

416
00:23:02,490 --> 00:23:04,370
you still have the right

417
00:23:04,370 --> 00:23:06,090
to choose?

418
00:23:06,610 --> 00:23:07,610
You must keep your promise.

419
00:23:07,780 --> 00:23:08,090
You!

420
00:23:08,700 --> 00:23:09,730
Sir, don’t give it to him.

421
00:23:09,730 --> 00:23:10,700
Don’t worry, girl.

422
00:23:15,940 --> 00:23:16,730
At last!

423
00:23:16,850 --> 00:23:19,210
At last, I’ve found what Lord wants!

424
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:23,300
Why is there a poem?

425
00:23:31,610 --> 00:23:32,820
Run!

426
00:23:34,540 --> 00:23:36,610
Sir! Sir!

427
00:23:37,610 --> 00:23:39,010
Run!

428
00:23:39,010 --> 00:23:39,850
Sir!

429
00:23:39,850 --> 00:23:41,210
Go! Hurry!

430
00:23:41,210 --> 00:23:42,060
Sir!

431
00:23:42,300 --> 00:23:43,420
Go!

432
00:23:45,250 --> 00:23:45,610
Go!

