00:23:51,940 --> 00:23:53,580
What did you do?

437
00:23:53,580 --> 00:23:55,210
Why is it burnt?

438
00:23:55,210 --> 00:23:56,730
You want to know?

439
00:23:57,580 --> 00:23:59,850
But I won’t tell you!

440
00:24:21,300 --> 00:24:22,660
It’s been nearly ten days.

441
00:24:22,660 --> 00:24:24,370
Still no message from that girl?

442
00:24:25,610 --> 00:24:27,490
If she travels fast,

443
00:24:27,490 --> 00:24:29,580
she has just arrived at the foot
of the snow mountain.

444
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:31,060
Be patient.

445
00:24:32,460 --> 00:24:33,460
Look at him.

446
00:24:33,460 --> 00:24:35,330
He’s such a good young man.

447
00:24:35,330 --> 00:24:36,490
He left us for years.

448
00:24:36,490 --> 00:24:38,490
When he comes back, he’s dying.

449
00:24:39,900 --> 00:24:41,610
If I knew it,

450
00:24:41,610 --> 00:24:43,330
I wouldn’t have given Anzhi to Wang Lin,

451
00:24:43,330 --> 00:24:45,490
no matter how he persuaded me.

452
00:24:45,490 --> 00:24:46,820
Anzhi decided

453
00:24:46,820 --> 00:24:48,730
where he would go.

454
00:24:48,730 --> 00:24:49,730
None of us

455
00:24:49,730 --> 00:24:51,250
could decide

456
00:24:51,250 --> 00:24:52,940
for him.

457
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:56,060
After the mutiny
against the former dynasty,

458
00:24:57,090 --> 00:24:58,820
Anzhi was saved and sent to us.

459
00:24:59,460 --> 00:25:02,330
None of us had raised a baby.

460
00:25:02,330 --> 00:25:05,130
We were busy taking care of him.

461
00:25:05,130 --> 00:25:06,940
When he first stood up,

462
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:08,210
he was this tall.

463
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:11,210
When he grew a bit up,

464
00:25:11,210 --> 00:25:12,820
he began to fool us around

465
00:25:12,820 --> 00:25:14,330
every day.

