00:25:14,330 --> 00:25:15,820
If I remember correctly,

467
00:25:16,490 --> 00:25:19,060
when Wang Lin found us,

468
00:25:19,060 --> 00:25:20,780
he was

469
00:25:20,780 --> 00:25:21,580
just this tall.

470
00:25:21,940 --> 00:25:22,490
Yes. Yes.

471
00:25:23,010 --> 00:25:23,900
Just this tall.

472
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:25,130
To my waist.

473
00:25:25,130 --> 00:25:25,780
Yes.

474
00:25:26,820 --> 00:25:28,060
At that time,

475
00:25:28,060 --> 00:25:30,610
