477
00:25:33,460 --> 00:25:36,460
I still remember that very clearly.

478
00:25:36,460 --> 00:25:38,180
We didn’t want that, of course.

479
00:25:38,180 --> 00:25:40,060
Everyone knew

480
00:25:40,060 --> 00:25:42,300
Wang Lin only wanted
to recover the former dynasty.

481
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:43,330
Later,

482
00:25:43,330 --> 00:25:45,370
you and his Junior Master told me

483
00:25:45,370 --> 00:25:47,370
if I didn’t let him go back,

484
00:25:47,370 --> 00:25:48,610
he would be a mere villager

485
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:51,130
on Penglai Island

486
00:25:51,130 --> 00:25:53,010
all his life.

487
00:25:54,370 --> 00:25:55,610
Even when he died,

488
00:25:55,610 --> 00:25:57,490
he would only think

489
00:25:57,490 --> 00:26:00,610
this small island was the whole world.

490
00:26:01,490 --> 00:26:03,850
His Junior Master loved him most.

491
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:06,210
But it was also him

492
00:26:06,210 --> 00:26:08,060
who urged him to leave.

493
00:26:08,060 --> 00:26:12,060
He said Anzhi couldn’t decide
where to live

494
00:26:12,060 --> 00:26:15,180
before he had enough experience.

495
00:26:16,130 --> 00:26:17,010
Could this be

496
00:26:18,300 --> 00:26:20,370
his final destiny?

497
00:26:23,090 --> 00:26:25,330
A generous man like him

498
00:26:25,850 --> 00:26:28,010
would not stay

499
00:26:28,010 --> 00:26:30,780
on Penglai Island

500
00:26:31,490 --> 00:26:32,780
and grew old

501
00:26:32,780 --> 00:26:34,300
with us.

502
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:36,700
It was his own choice.

503
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:38,700
It was also his fate.

504
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:40,660
Besides,

505
00:26:41,330 --> 00:26:42,850
if he didn’t go,

506
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:45,090
he wouldn’t have met the girl

507
00:26:45,090 --> 00:26:47,090
who is taking a great risk

508
00:26:47,090 --> 00:26:50,010
to find the Fire Lotus for him.

509
00:26:53,010 --> 00:26:53,660
Fei.

510
00:26:57,130 --> 00:26:58,130
Be careful, Fei!

511
00:26:59,460 --> 00:27:00,210
Fei.

512
00:27:04,490 --> 00:27:05,780
I met that girl.

513
00:27:07,250 --> 00:27:08,730
She’s faithful.

514
00:27:08,730 --> 00:27:10,210
Anzhi has a good taste.

515
00:27:49,180 --> 00:27:50,850
If Tongming is right,

516
00:27:51,300 --> 00:27:54,250
