544
00:29:38,210 --> 00:29:38,820
What do you think?

545
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:42,660
Funny.

546
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:45,370
Since when did I need you

547
00:29:45,370 --> 00:29:47,010
to make a concession?

548
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:49,330
