553
00:30:07,130 --> 00:30:08,850
You don’t want to wait
for another decade, huh?

554
00:30:09,540 --> 00:30:10,660
Don’t touch it!

555
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:13,580
If you want it,

556
00:30:14,250 --> 00:30:15,820
give me the Seal of Cautiousness.

557
00:30:15,820 --> 00:30:17,580
