for the Seal of Cautiousness!

559
00:30:20,330 --> 00:30:21,970
Don’t you want it?

560
00:30:23,490 --> 00:30:25,130
Why don’t we cooperate

561
00:30:25,130 --> 00:30:25,900
and get it from her?

